mission.gis: Work in teams to capture and control as many territories as possible.
md: Work in teams to control the land. Capture a territory to start
racking up points: the team with the most points wins - or you
can win outright by capturing every territory.~n~~n~8 Teams~n~

string: Help your team defend the territories
Capture territories to gain points, or take all to win.
More team members taking a territory will speed up the capturing time.
If territory is contested, clear enemies to secure capture.
